metadata.name: Triptych
metadata.description:
While walking in the illuminated streets of such a lively city, we write our own story. A reality that we can shape as we idealize it, where all our desires are finally within reach.

Immerse yourself in the sea of glowing lights, let it bring you to a state where your emotions are out of control.

Shinjuku, Tokyo. June 19th, 2021.
5889 x 4000px
